Didn't really notice any drop in performance, so that's great. Vuze can be used as an alternative to WebTorrent.Desktop, especially when it comes to seeding massive amounts of torrents using WebRTC. Peer discovery seems to take an awful lot of time with only one client seeding, having said that..
&nbsp;
WebTorrent.Desktop is a good application, don't get me wrong. It also downloads torrents a lot faster than even Bittorrent. Then again, it's only really suitable for 1-5 files, or if you really wanna get your files out there, or to stream BitTorrent files before they even download. You sacrifice GPU but you get top speed, which is useful in some cases.

